  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317330/extras/45f68c587fa821a733c142fb335ec451.poster.avif?t=1772829617\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317330/extras/45f68c587fa821a733c142fb335ec451.webm?t=1772829617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317330/extras/45f68c587fa821a733c142fb335ec451.mp4?t=1772829617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Who Are You?</h2>A woman who killed herself.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Where Are You?</h2>In 3 surreal hexagon rooms.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Are In These Rooms?</h2>Secret messages to decode, hidden clues to jot down, Morse code to translate, equations to solve ... and around <strong>2 - 3 hours</strong> of unique, hand-crafted puzzles that will put your problem-solving skills to the test.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Why Are You Here?</h2>To uncover a tragic incident and the events that led to my death.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Else?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A parrot to feed</li><li>A piano to play</li><li>A plantable seed</li><li>A picture to take</li><li>An ear to listen</li><li>A heart to give</li><li>A chair on the floor</li><li>And many more</li><li>(No cats)</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317330/extras/45f68c587fa821a733c142fb335ec451.poster.avif?t=1772829617\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317330/extras/45f68c587fa821a733c142fb335ec451.webm?t=1772829617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317330/extras/45f68c587fa821a733c142fb335ec451.mp4?t=1772829617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Who Are You?</h2>A woman who killed herself.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Where Are You?</h2>In 3 surreal hexagon rooms.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Are In These Rooms?</h2>Secret messages to decode, hidden clues to jot down, Morse code to translate, equations to solve ... and around <strong>2 - 3 hours</strong> of unique, hand-crafted puzzles that will put your problem-solving skills to the test.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Why Are You Here?</h2>To uncover a tragic incident and the events that led to my death.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Else?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A parrot to feed</li><li>A piano to play</li><li>A plantable seed</li><li>A picture to take</li><li>An ear to listen</li><li>A heart to give</li><li>A chair on the floor</li><li>And many more</li><li>(No cats)</li></ul>",
